Sentencas: A new design of high-porosity substrates with large gas permeability for segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cells (SIS-SOFCs) is presented in this paper.
Titulo: Large gas permeability nickel/alumina substrates with hierarchical pore structure for solid oxide fuel cells derived from particle-stabilized emulsions
